<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's expecting her third child with her husband, TV host Grant Denyer.</p>

<p>And on Sunday, Chezzi Denyer flaunted her growing baby bump as she paid tribute to her 'main man' on Father's Day.</p>

<p>'Happy Father's Day to the main man in our lives,' she captioned a photo of herself posing with Grant and their two daughters, Scout and Sailor.</p>

<p>Incoming! Chezzi Denyer flaunted her growing baby bump as she shared a sweet Father's Day tribute to her husband, Grant. The couple are pictured with their daughters, Scout and Sailor</p>

<p>Chezzi, 42, added: 'Grant makes every day feel special!' </p>

<p>In the photo, the proud family of four posing together while Scout, four, and Sailor, eight, touch their mother's belly.</p>

<p>It comes days after Chezzi revealed her pregnancy cravings had started to kick in. </p>

<p>'Happy Father's Day to the main man in our lives,' she wrote while tagging Grant. '[Grant] who makes everyday feel special!' she continued.</p>

